I wanted to personally thank everyone who’s ordered their copy of ‘Bodyscapes’. Your support means the world to me 🙏

Unfortunately there has been a production delay in the printing process and the estimated shipping date is now mid Jan. I’m very sorry for the hold up and will continue to do everything I can to get your books to you ASAP.

To thank you all for your patience I have decided to include a signed print for all pre orders, not just the first 100. I can’t wait to get these books to you and will keep you updated as I begin to ship out.
When you live in a van the world is your backyard

Some Polaroids from my upcoming book ‘Bodyscapes’. 

All pre-orders include a signed print of one of the polaroids featured in the book 💙⚡️

The ‘Bodyscapes’ Collector’s Edition is now available for purchase. 

Each of these limited edition of 18 red covers comes with a signed original Polaroid and unique hand alterations throughout the book.

There’s something beautiful about holding a tangible book in our ever growing digital world. There’s also something beautiful in sharing what you’ve created with one of your biggest inspirations. Cheers @ryanmcginleystudios !
